Further, explicit ANM calculations with chiral NN and 3N interactions (56, 68, 69) have"
shown that the asymmetry dependence of the nuclear EOS is reasonably well reproduced
"by the standard quadratic approximation E(n, δ)/A = E(n, 0)/A + Esym(n) δ
